  "keyFeatures": [
    "Sparse BM25 retrieval with DuckDB, SQLite, and PostgreSQL backends",
    "Dense vector retrieval using cosine similarity with DuckDB and PostgreSQL",
    "Hybrid retrieval via Reciprocal Rank Fusion (RRF) with DuckDB and PostgreSQL",
    "Text tokenization via Pyserini's Lucene Analyzer",
    "JSONL and Parquet data format support",
    "CLI and Python API interfaces",
    "Reproducible IR experiments on BEIR benchmarks",
    "Environment variable configuration via dotenv"
